# Dotfiles

Managed with rcm: https://github.com/thoughtbot/rcm

http://robots.thoughtbot.com/rcm-for-rc-files-in-dotfiles-repos

```
# Install RCM
brew tap thoughtbot/formulae
brew install rcm
```

```
lsrc # Init

rcup # link
```

# Install sexy-bash-prompt (https://github.com/twolfson/sexy-bash-prompt)
`(cd /tmp && git clone --depth 1 https://github.com/twolfson/sexy-bash-prompt && cd sexy-bash-prompt && make
install) && source ~/.bashrc`

